verbose_text: In a recent study of 31 novel biomarkers, Salomaa et al. demonstrated an association between clinically incident diabetes and insulin receptor, creatine kinase-MB, MR-Pro atrial natriuretic peptide, NT-Pro B-type natriuretic peptide, and B-type natriuretic peptide.
evidence: association between clinically incident diabetes and insulin receptor, creatine kinase-MB, MR-Pro atrial natriuretic peptide, NT-Pro B-type natriuretic peptide, and B-type natriuretic peptide
